BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Putting Assets to Work Communitywide Meeting
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260225T180000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260225T200000
UID:371e547b5d053c73728840cda7c3bd97@cityofevanston.org
DESCRIPTION:<div class="detail-content">The City is looking for your input
 ! Putting Assets to Work (PAW) is Evanston&rsquo\;s initiative for communi
 ty-driven asset development. Using crowdsourced placemaking&mdash\;digital
  platforms\, community meetings\, surveys\, and focus groups&mdash\;we gat
 her ideas that directly shape how City properties are improved and used. Y
 our participation helps ensure public assets benefit all Evanston resident
 s\, from longtime community members to new arrivals of every age and backg
 round.</div>
LOCATION:Robert Crown Community Center\, 1801 Main Street
X-SOURCE:City of Evanston Meetings
END:VEVENT
